i know what they do, mana songs, charm songs, haste and melee stats songs....i was wondering, do most bards past level lets say 15 use melee, i used to have one and i was totally surprised how bad a beating they take considering they can weild great weapons and wear impressive armor.<P>as far as i know bards are story tellers and musicians, i want to know what they mean in everquest.<P>this isnt a put down post, i really want to hear what high level bards have to say, eq has me confused about bards<P>also what are good stats for a bard? str cant be one because they dont seem to melee very well. i was going to assume stamina and dex, am i wrong?
