<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
I don't know about meele, I found that at level 15 or so we go through a meele deficit untill you get dual weild. I only used attks for a bit of damage but didn't find things went too well and just keept my head low. Then at level 17 and 18 things went back up with dual weild and DDD, I started to kick ass again. Though the best I must say is level 20 when you get AoE slow song whith AC debuff. Makes you a decent tank since things hit you less often and interupt you singing less often with their rude bashing.  <IMG SRC="rolleyes.gif" border="0"> .<P>Anyway your not much of a tank right now, just sit tight use the lullaby to keep things from overwelming you and don't be afraid to back off. And the most important thing keep selos memorized, the nothing really wimpy from running from a fight and comming back in a minute to kill them off after regrouping.<P>Good luck to you and don't give up, tanking will be yours again (make sure you get some banded though  <IMG SRC="wink.gif" border="0"> .<P>--------------------<P>Carlota<BR>Tallon Zek Server
