oever.  Enchanters can NEVER keep up that kind of kill rate EVER.  Even though I was only getting 1 kill worth of exp every 2 minutes which is still very hard for enchanters I also almost never even got hit or anything and when I did I could always heal no problem while my pet was fighting, I also heal way faster with the bard and can do it while fighting also I run way faster than my ENC.  I also cast while running which helps immensely.  We do have a lock on charming believe it or not.<P>Tsunamii Starshine<BR>52 Enchantress Rallos Zek<BR>Breakdancer Tsunamii<BR>29 Bard Rallos Zek<P>--------------------<P>Tsunamii Starshine
