BTW Tinolan, All the tests the enchanter community has done come up with one conclusion, CHA has NO effect on charming.  All the tests show a maximum gain of ~5% and some have decreased effectiveness from higher CHA.  Since empyrical data can only be 95% accurate this 5% +/- sway means there is NO difference in the data set with 200CHA and the one with 80.<P>Tsunamii Starshine<P>--------------------<P>Tsunamii Starshine
